{"tid":1649014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣建議 back to simple","createTime":"2019-10-12T12:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T15:35:17.000Z","uid":142716,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"36002267634eed489adb7a4a79267852ffe5fa1d","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"其實文宣組整啲文宣真係整得好靚嫁<br />\n但係眼見文宣傳到出街嘅真係少左好多<br />\n明明6, 7月嗰時好多文宣嫁喎！淨係出街搭個車都會收到airdrop<br />\n我地要記住，依場運動唔只有後生仔參加，<br />\n好多人都無睇開連登同tg嫁，<br />\n不如我地繼續痴牆同落街派文宣啊！<br />\n無資源印、無時間派，唔緊要，<br />\nfacebook有啦掛！仲有airdrop呢！<br />\n要將所有文宣活動推廣哂去唔同年齡層啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過連登行動post都要繼續推，太多五毛，搞到行動post推極都唔上</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋想比多建議，大型遊行集會要早啲吹雞，<br />\n要多啲時間發酵先聚到更多人<br />\n同埋姐姐哥哥無小朋友咁好氣好力，<br />\n落完街散步，臨時第二日又有活動係比較吃力嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己follow開嘅文宣channel：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9hmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=d2f9806a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9hmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=11cf5a52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日活動</span></span>！<br />\n我都係琴晚見到tg有，所以急推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開左個post推極都唔郁，趁依家推多次<br />\n記住！！要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傳出同溫層啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>facebook、ig、連儂牆、派文宣、airdrop，總知用你嘅方法</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n共和黨參議員Ted Cruz都嚟埋香港啦，<br />\n香港人唔係唔出下話？<br />\nSir, this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjxoRUK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfjxoRUK.jpg&h=05b4d53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnXXbUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnXXbUL.jpg&h=f1638a01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"177a869500f6a5843ea18b1b773b340cbf5ab1c7","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"8be63f430e8e86b81aa27a67330e259ee4f44767","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"abe81e8d379de70ec249dbce55ff6cb099383ac2","tid":1649014,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0c115263b3b5896fc5fb1b36cb5598fbf9c8e5b","tid":1649014,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd305547d1982fc0e084c913e285aa89fe300656","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"045cba7a6607fa6362487fd4e3c3022f40a675cc","tid":1649014,"uid":287594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"[行動POST] 想要靚畫面？銀髮族48小時靜坐咪就係機會囉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648992</a><br />\n<br />\n警總靜坐現場，有老人有中年人有外國人有後生仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多中年帶哂席同櫈黎，準備過夜。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">想有新行動？想要靚畫面？咁你就快啲過黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日攰唔出都唔緊要，準備聽日接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我煲大佢，唔好當銀髮手足係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAwXWg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAwXWg8.jpg&h=aab0f8a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f21c2b20a8739bbeaee2898c472b8934d15dbb2","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"dce78b8ac8b64e0f0cb8ee52810890e148b6a62d","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"1f4b960d271c084d993c15fc2cf97b6f6168bdc6","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"c7ae113f6ef41cca37333bc2ae85dc3c896ef20d","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"bd848c827dab18e35b4c7be761c86782a242fa64","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"c048bda58aebf6f0cc6998b583b02d2d70a50c09","tid":1649014,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"405e2f67995b578d0c656b887162ebc7e10dff46","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:03:21.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"e82e3fa5da8fc29d3762589dabd11070c87d3b81","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"b9fecc80b9b2e2d818961a5744cec05236b4c4ee","tid":1649014,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"